---
// About and contact section with structured data for local business
---

<section
  class="relative py-32 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[800px]"
  data-purpose="about-contact"
  id="hikayemiz"
>
  <!-- Parallax Background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <div class="w-full h-full img-skeleton">
      <img
        alt="Zeynep Ticaret mağaza iç mekanı ve ürün sergileme"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        src="footer.jpg"
        width="1200"
        height="800"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-stone-900/30"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Glassmorphism Card -->
  <div
    class="relative z-10 w-[95%] max-w-5xl glass-card rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl flex flex-col md:flex-row reveal-observer"
    id="iletisim"
  >
    <!-- Left: Story -->
    <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 md:w-3/5 border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-stone-200">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl mb-8">Bizim Hikayemiz</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          12 yıllık köklü tecrübemizle Denizli'nin kalbinde başlayan yolculuğumuzda, yerel butik anlayışını modern ev dekorasyonuyla buluşturuyoruz. <strong class="text-stone-900">Zeynep Ticaret</strong> olarak, sadece eşya satmıyor, müşteri memnuniyetini odağımıza alarak yaşam alanlarınıza ruh katacak en "uygun" ve "kaliteli" parçaları özenle seçiyoruz.
        </p>
        <p>
          Geleneksel ticaretin samimiyetini ve 12 senelik güven bağını dijital dünyanın hızıyla birleştirerek, ikas altyapılı mağazamız üzerinden Türkiye'nin her noktasına mutluluk ulaştırıyoruz. Modern, estetik ve bütçe dostu çözümlerimizle evinizdeki huzurlu dokunuşun adresi olmaya devam ediyoruz.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4 items-center">
        <!-- Store Button -->
        <a
          href="https://store.zeynepticaretdenizli.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="px-6 py-3 bg-stone-900 text-white rounded-full font-bold text-sm tracking-wide uppercase hover:bg-stone-800 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:translate-y-0"
        >
          Mağazayı Gez
        </a>
        <!-- Brand Badge -->
        <div
          class="px-4 py-2 bg-stone-100 rounded-full font-bold text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-stone-400 border border-stone-200"
        >
          IKAS Partner
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Contact -->
    <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 md:w-2/5 flex flex-col justify-between bg-stone-50/50">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl mb-8">Bize Ulaşın</h2>
        <address class="space-y-6 not-italic">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-1">Adres</p>
            <p class="text-stone-900 font-medium italic">
              Hacıkaplanlar, Barış Cd. No:34, 20100 Pamukkale/Denizli
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:gap-12 gap-6">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-1">Telefon</p>
              <a
                href="tel:+905383045524"
                class="text-stone-900 font-medium hover:text-stone-700 transition-colors"
              >
                0538 304 55 24
              </a>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-1">Sosyal Medya</p>
              <div class="flex gap-4 mt-1">
                <a
                  href="https://www.instagram.com/zeynepticarett/"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="text-stone-900 hover:text-[#E4405F] transition-colors"
                  title="Instagram"
                >
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266.057 1.645.069 4.849.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zm0 5.838c-3.403 0-6.162 2.759-6.162 6.162s2.759 6.163 6.162 6.163 6.162-2.759 6.162-6.163c0-3.403-2.759-6.162-6.162-6.162zm0 10.162c-2.209 0-4-1.791-4-4 0-2.209 1.791-4 4-4s4 1.791 4 4c0 2.209-1.791 4-4 4zm6.406-11.845c-.796 0-1.441.645-1.441 1.44s.645 1.44 1.441 1.44c.795 0 1.439-.645 1.439-1.44s-.644-1.44-1.439-1.44z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </a>
                <a
                  href="https://www.facebook.com/zeynepticaretz"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="text-stone-900 hover:text-[#1877F2] transition-colors"
                  title="Facebook"
                >
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </address>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 space-y-4">
        <a
          class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 w-full bg-[#25D366] text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all"
          href="https://wa.me/905383045524"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          title="WhatsApp ile iletişim kurun"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-6 h-6 fill-current"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          WhatsApp ile Sorun
        </a>
        <p class="text-[10px] text-center text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-widest">
          Çalışma Saatleri: 09:00 - 19:00
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
